name: Title In Progress
description:
Sound is absolutely essential to play this game! Please play with sound on! Join 🌸Natalie🌸, 🏹Mark🏹, and ♈Wanderdust♈ as they speak their new game into existence! Play as the main character as you try to make your way through a game that's constantly changing around you.  Whose ideas will stay in the game? Play "Title In Progress" and find out! ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ Jason Rand- Programming (191 coins) Catherine Rand - Art DanzMacabre - Wanderdust, Music, Sound Design, Story (139 coins) Jillian Wagner - Natalie, Story (102 coins) Willis Reifsnyder - Mark, Story, Additional Voices (168 coins)

All Art, Music, and Gameplay was made for specifically for the Brackeys Game Jam.
